page.title: 03BUILDINGS AROUND WOODBORO 2
page.content: type"windows add variety to the modern streets.This is so on Ploughman Avenue-a cul de sac, next to this are eight such cottages, and next to these is a house still under construction!Near Doverbeck Drive is a Baptist Church dated 1835.It is small and reminiscent of a cottage.On the outskirts of Woodborough lie the executive bungalows_these expensive bungalows were, in 1986 valued at Â£90,ooo. They are set away from the road with extensive garden space {NEW DEVELOPMENTS Woodborough is expanding and there are many "new developments".Broad Close has been constructed within the last year;some houses are finished but some are still under construction.Also,on the corner of foxwood lane an old army camp is being made into flats.
